column2:
ComCare has the following objectives:1. To provide assistance to Singapore citizens and permanent residents of Singapore and their family members living in Singapore who are in financial or other difficulties to enable them to:> >  * attain sufficient income to meet their basic needs;
 * address the development issues faced by their children;
 * facilitate their integration into society



2. To develop programmes to enhance the capacity of the community to undertake the objectives mentioned above.
